<L>__{exterior stephen's cathedral vienna a rainy day 1790's}
<A>__{the lacrimosa continues through all of the following: a small group of people emerges from the side door into the raw, wet day, accompanying a cheap wooden coffin. the coffin is borne by a gravedigger and schikaneder in mourning clothes. they load it onto a cart, drawn by a poor black horse. all the rest are in black, also: salieri, von swieten, constanze and her son, karl, madame weber and her youngest daughter sophie, and even lorl, the maid. it is drizzling. the cart sets off. the group follows.}
